      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Consider customizing how your spells look when you can cast them. Your Lorehold spells might create displays of golden light. You might use a tome or a scroll as a spellcasting focus, and your spell effects might reflect the appearance of the reference books you study."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "h1",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Building a Lorehold Character"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Any class or subclass that deals with knowledge of the past can be a good fit for Lorehold. "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Bards"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " thrive in Lorehold, and "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Wizards"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " (particularly those of the "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "School of Divination"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ") are numerous among its students. "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Clerics"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " (often with the "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Knowledge"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " or "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Light"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " domains) are also quite common."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For a more unusual take on a Lorehold student, you could consider playing a "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Barbarian"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " with a primal connection to the past (perhaps adopting the "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Path of the Ancestral Guardian"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ") or a "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Paladin"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " whose "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Oath of the Ancients"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " gives a concrete link to history."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "em",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Suggested Characteristics."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " Methodical historians and daring adventurers alike can be found among the ranks of Lorehold college. The Lorehold Personality Traits table suggests a variety of traits you might adopt for your character."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Lorehold Personality Traits"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "table",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "th",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "d6"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "th",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Personality Trait"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "1"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I thrive on esoteric lore. The more obscure the historical references I can include in everyday conversation, the better."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "2"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "By searching for these lost artifacts, I hope to find who I really am along the way."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "3"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I can barely go a minute without talking about my research. I have so much knowledge in my head, and it needs to be let out somewhere!"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "4"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The spirits of the dead are so much more interesting to talk with than living classmates."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "5"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I can speak eloquently about the historical ramifications of an ancient war. But ask me to add two-digit numbers together, and I'm a mess."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "6"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "In the end, it's all just entropy. Everything falls apart someday."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
